# Styling and UI Guidelines

## Tailwind CSS Configuration

- **Version**: Tailwind CSS v4 with PostCSS
- **Configuration**: [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) with ShadCN color system
- **CSS Variables**: HSL color system with CSS custom properties
- **RTL Support**: Use `rtl:` and `ltr:` prefixes for directional styles

## ShadCN UI Components

- **Configuration**: [components.json](mdc:components.json) for ShadCN setup
- **Components**: Located in [components/ui/](mdc:components/ui/) directory
- **Available Components**: Button, Card, Input, Label, Dialog
- **Installation**: Use `bunx shadcn@latest add <component>` to add new components

## Color System

### CSS Variables (HSL Format)
```css
:root {
  --background: 0 0% 100%;
  --foreground: 222.2 84% 4.9%;
  --primary: 222.2 47.4% 11.2%;
  --secondary: 210 40% 96%;
  --muted: 210 40% 96%;
  --accent: 210 40% 96%;
  --destructive: 0 84.2% 60.2%;
  --border: 214.3 31.8% 91.4%;
  --input: 214.3 31.8% 91.4%;
  --ring: 222.2 84% 4.9%;
  --radius: 0.5rem;
}
```

### Dark Mode Support
- Automatic dark mode with `.dark` class
- All colors have dark mode variants
- Use `dark:` prefix for dark mode specific styles

